<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>纽约时报 &amp;gt; 美国 &amp;gt; 政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/spotlight/on-politics</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 02:50:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>佛罗里达州的选区重划战争、佐治亚州的决选和最新的政治新闻</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/06/us/politics/redistricting-virginia-florida-ga-special-election-republicans.html</link><description>随着未来两周最后期限的临近，两者都没有完全按照党派计划进行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 21:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/06/us/politics/redistricting-virginia-florida-ga-special-election-republicans.html</guid></item><item><title>随着民主党在中期选举前变得乐观，六场参议院竞选值得关注</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/03/us/politics/senate-races-midterms-primary-election.html</link><description>对于该党来说，夺回控制权仍然是一项艰巨的任务。这是最新的。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 15:41:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/03/us/politics/senate-races-midterms-primary-election.html</guid></item><item><title>特朗普支持的路易斯安那州初选候选人也赞扬了 DEI。会伤害她吗？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/01/us/politics/julia-letlow-louisiana-republican-primary.html</link><description>路易斯安那州众议员朱莉娅·莱特洛 (Julia Letlow) 正在竞选挑战参议员比尔·卡西迪 (Bill Cassidy)，她因 2020 年的言论而面临保守派的反击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 21:39:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/01/us/politics/julia-letlow-louisiana-republican-primary.html</guid></item><item><title>缅因州、密歇根州及其他地区初选速成班</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/primary-elections-maine-michigan.html</link><description>这是关于接下来要发生的事情的速成课程。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 23:41:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/primary-elections-maine-michigan.html</guid></item><item><title>CPAC 考虑万斯、卢比奥和特朗普之后的生活</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/27/us/politics/cpac-trump-vance-rubio.html</link><description>一位与会者表示，总统的潜在继任者“都是凡人”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 21:53:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/27/us/politics/cpac-trump-vance-rubio.html</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的主要批评者、众议员托马斯·马西能在肯塔基州初选中坚持下去吗？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/us/politics/thomas-massie-trump.html</link><description>任何共和党人都可以不同意特朗普的观点并侥幸逃脱惩罚吗？托马斯·马西在肯塔基州的初选是一个关键考验。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 22:19:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/us/politics/thomas-massie-trump.html</guid></item><item><title>这是美国的一个混乱时刻。这不是共和党人需要的。</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/politics/republicans-trump-midterms.html</link><description>重大选举前的全国性不安和焦虑情绪对执政党来说很少有好处。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 22:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/politics/republicans-trump-midterms.html</guid></item><item><title>由于“丛林初选”，加州可能会选举共和党州长</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/20/us/politics/california-primary-gop-governors-race.html</link><description>该州完全开放的“丛林初选”让民主党人感到紧张。</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 21:18:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/20/us/politics/california-primary-gop-governors-race.html</guid></item><item><title>伊利诺伊州比赛最热闹的结果</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/18/us/politics/what-happened-illinois-election.html</link><description>以下是候选人观看派对上最佳复出、最自豪的州长和最昂贵的水的摘要。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 13:52:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/18/us/politics/what-happened-illinois-election.html</guid></item><item><title>伊利诺伊州初选民主党内讧的内幕</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/politics/illinois-democrat-primary-brandon-herrera-mamdani.html</link><description>我们与皮奥里亚出生的记者谈论了他声称是美国最好的州的小学日。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 21:44:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/politics/illinois-democrat-primary-brandon-herrera-mamdani.html</guid></item></channel></rss>